body:
@perv.sensei
Glad it worked out for you two. 
Seiya lost sight of what was important. He let his lust and pride get the best of him. He became callous, and this uncaring personality led him to make mistakes concerning the heart of Suzu. Raping so many girls weakened his pairing hormones, leading to his cold-hearted rejection of Suzu. Had he exercised just a modicum of self-control and only ever got sexually involved with Suzu, he could have had a happy life with her. But he doomed himself instead. What a fool.
